Provides basic functionality to support i18n.

Installation
-------------
Normal NetBeans plugin installation.

Future. welcome contributors :)
-------------------------------
- Hint fix that will automatically extracts string literals to a specified Bundle.properties
- Configuration of the Suppression string from NetBeans Option windows
- To fix the issue when there are more than 1 string literal found in a line.
  2 hints will be displayed a the moment.

